{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6897942d1b","title":"关于宣传工作的一封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"673dce2a26","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":13,"articleId":"6897942d1b","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"新闻广播和出版","id":"268718f23b","type":"主题"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"林彪","id":"cce608ea44","type":"主题"},{"name":"个人崇拜","id":"eb3ed1b86b","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"88219c53be","type":"title","text":"关于宣传工作的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"824e1eed06","type":"paragraph","text":"军委各总部、各军兵种、各军区：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f05478040","type":"paragraph","text":"关于宣传工作问题，多年来，我曾向《解放军报》、《人民日报》负责同志多次谈过宣传内容问题，就是要在—切埸合和宣传的各种方式，都应突出对毛主席的宣传，对毛主席思想和毛上席革命路线的宣传，而不要宣传我。为此，特重新提出以下各点，盼同志们严格注意：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"06583f050c","type":"paragraph","text":"一、不要在街上和刊物中，宣传“树立林副主席的崇高威望”的口号。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6854da6a3c","type":"paragraph","text":"二、不要出我的语录和文集。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3bc4d2effb","type":"paragraph","text":"三、戏剧、电影、小说中，不要有叙述我的革命历史的事迹。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc98d8122d","type":"paragraph","text":"四、不要呼喊“祝林副主席永远健康”的口号。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d459190c37","type":"paragraph","text":"五、最近各地开学习毛主席著作积极分子会，要求我题词均很多。鉴于最近一次题词引起了个别地方两派的纠粉，因此，一概不再题词了。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3956091d25","type":"paragraph","text":"六、应大力突出宣传毛主席和党十央，最好完全不要提到我。在万—需要提到我时，也无论如何不可超过十分之一的比例。这样，才能造成宣传的统一性和集中性。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2c779adfa1","type":"paragraph","text":"以上各点，盼在营以上干部中印发传到，务必落实。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"257248410b","type":"paragraph","text":"（部队发到营以上，地方发到县以上）","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d60a316fd","type":"paragraph","text":"林  彪","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b85075f2d5","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年十二月十三日","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6897942d1b","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}